          And the main menu for i.group returns.

          If the user responds n, the menu containing the group
          files after it was modified will be displayed and the
          user will be asked to place an x in front of those that
          are to be removed from the group.  Then, a menu listing
          all of the other cell in the  current MAPSET will be
